Mana Sieve was a tool that was very helpful when it arrived.  The original way to kill Lady Vox (who Cheals) was to have at least 3 Chanters Mana Sieving her to limit her heals.  Your chanter mana would be nil, but so what....you aren't doing any damage anyway.  Mobs like Gore followed this pattern in their day.<br>
<br>
Over time, this spell has become less useful.  Wandering Mind, Theft of Thought and Scryer's Tresspass are all Mana Taps albeit the have very long recasts.  Their just are not (generally speaking) the issues with mobs like Vox today.  Yeah their are still caster mobs, but people dont generally sieve them.<br>
<br>
