at does not use mana.   So you can sieve Vox all way down, but she'll still cast breath.<br>
<br>
But heals, gates, etc are all mana based.   Whenever you fight a healing mob, especially one that doesn't stun well, mana sieve is great.   Mob mana pools are not that large.    <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bregalad Alcarin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, High Elf Phantasmist, Xev &lt;Legends of Westwood&gt;<br>
